{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"海啸——为英雄古巴高唱三首歌","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":11,"day":12}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为英雄古巴高唱三首歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间献给海上舵手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"折不断的帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打不断的篙；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊涛骇浪中间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨帆升得更高；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的风帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远不降落。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕十二级风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕千丈潮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是天生的奴隶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会被海盗吓倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加勒比海的舵手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天地风云一手招，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪头上拥出大砍刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进战胜大风暴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海　　啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一支号角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要发出呼号："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风呵跟我走吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪呵随我奔跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要放声高歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号召所有的江河："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了革命向前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来把暗礁冲破。结成天罗地网，齐把海盗封锁。地球要开红花，花开不能摘掉。滚滚浪涛冲天起，风声阵阵海长啸。吉隆滩颂七百万颗心灵上，都有一座橄榄园；猫头鹰儿嘴巴尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢不走树上绿橄榄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七百万双手上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有一座吉隆滩；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任它惊涛拍岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上红星色不变。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风暴雨里能看到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那最坚定的容颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吉隆滩呵吉隆滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山动海摇你不动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吉隆滩呵吉隆滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了敌人一刀砍！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1962年10月，肯尼迪海盗非法宣布对古巴实行军事封锁后作）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}